Description:
CLOSE TO EVERYTHING - POTENIAL SUB DIVISION - STCA
Attention investors, developers and home buyers!!! This priceless gem is perfectly suited to buyers who are looking for a home to move into, investment property to add to their portfolio or potential sub-division (STCA) - the opportunities are endless!
Built on 788 sqm corner block, this home has plenty to offer complete with Spacious living area, three good sized bedrooms, with a light and bright central bathroom. The kitchen includes gas cook top, oven and abundance of cupboard space all overlooking the open plan dining area with separate toilet. .
Its positioned in a superb location - walking distance to Schools, Central Werribee, cafes, Restaurants and 500m from Werribee Train Station.
Set on 788sqm land, there is a garage at the rear of the property making an ideal for any buyer who needs extra storage for a caravan, boat, cars, trailers or machinery.
This property is perfect for any developer who is looking for a property in a prime location, you can leave the original home and build a 2nd dwelling at the rear or can accommodate 4 new townhouses (STCA)

Approx. 788sqm land - potential sub-division (STCA)

500m to Werribee CBD

Description:
The Premium Point Cook Experience
LJ Hooker Point Cook presents 4 Sandy Avenue, Point Cook. If space is luxury, this palatial residence delivers in spaces. Timelessly appealing and of the highest quality, this exquisite property comprises five living zones, a magnificent kitchen, four bedrooms plus study, four-point-five bathrooms and accommodation for three vehicles. Masterfully designed by Porter Davis, this award-winning floorplan accommodates families of all sizes with 47 squares (approx.) of internal living. Nestled within an exclusive enclave of the Saltwater Coast Estate and with easy access to every convenience, this property delivers the premium Point Cook experience.
- Devine from the moment you step inside, the glorious ground floor encompasses a formal living room, open plan family and meals zone and a home theatre. Attention to detail is evident at every turn, with classically beautiful fixtures, upgraded chandelier lighting, a separate study, cloak room and powder room.
- At the heart of the home, the expertly crafted kitchen takes center stage, with glossy 2pac cabinetry, designer splash back, 40mm stone countertops, breakfast bar and walk-in-pantry. Both the kitchen and butlers galley are appointed with state-of-the-art stainless-steel appliances including an upright gas cooker, an additional gas cooktop, two canopy rangehoods and a dishwasher.
- Ascending the ornate timber staircase, the upper level offers a rumpus room plus a total of four bedrooms, each generous in size, with walk-in-robes, en suite bathrooms and plush carpets underfoot.
- The master suite is a private sanctuary, with an outdoor terrace, his and hers walk-in-robes and a decadent en suite of hotel quality, with dual vanity basins and a deluxe spa bath.
- Beautifully landscaped, the lush and low maintenance 600m2 (approx.) block is overlooked by the extensive covered patio, spanning two lengths of the home, the perfect place to entertain family and friends.
- The grounds offer side access and an outdoor shed, alongside a double remote-control garage with internal access.
- This immaculate property includes an internal laundry with storage, a walk-in-linen closet, zoned ducted gas heating, refrigerated cooling, ducted vacuum, solar panels, security alarm with video intercom, designer window dressings and downlights throughout.
Surrounded by quality homes, the master planned Saltwater Coast Estate offers residents access to the first-class lifestyle center, with a pool, tennis courts, function room and café. An abundance of neighborhood amenities includes quality schools, such as St Mary of the Cross Catholic Primary School, Saltwater P-9 College and Point Cook South Senior School. Attractions include Point Cook Coastal Park and bay, the Saltwater Coast Wetlands and Saltwater Community Centre. Public transportation options include the nearby Williams Landing train station and well-serviced bus routes, while shopping precincts include Sanctuary Lakes Shopping Centre.
Note. All stated dimensions are approximate only. Particulars given are for general information only and do not constitute any representation on the part of the vendor or agent.

Description:
Brand New Luxurious Home in Truganina P-9 School Zone
Ace Real Estate is proud to present 23 Ajax St Truganina. Spectacular in location, uncompromising in quality and just completed, this brand new brilliance is sure to impress you.
This divine Deco home is your garden paradise in the heart of Truganina; within a stroll of the strip and a skip of the schools, shopping centre. This magnificent single level home appointed with luxurious inclusions comprises of four bedroom, 2 bathrooms, dual living beauty offers today's entertaining lifestyle with a fine formal lounge, an airy family zone with a classic stainless-steel appliances and stone bench tops and double garage.
Starring an expertly-designed master bedroom with ensuite and walk in robe with central heating and cooling. This home is beautifully detailed with a stunning facade, high ceilings and artful Deco detail. Walk the kids to school; grab a latte on the way home, find the station & parklands close to home...find heaven in this divine Deco!
This is a good opportunity for first home buyers to buy Brand New home and claim first home buyer grant.
This character filled property is sure to impress with its magnificent establishment and huge list of luxurious appointments:
• Grand master bedroom with walk in robes and full en-suite.
• 3 Bedrooms with built in robes
• Formal Lounge
• Double garage with internal access & rear access.
• Stunning kitchen with abundance of cupboard space, walk in pantry, and stone bench top, 900 mm stainless steel appliances and dishwasher.
• Open plan family and meals.
• Central bathroom well connected to other bedrooms.
• Ducted heating and cooling.
• Low maintenance front and back yards.
Other exclusive extras include: Square set cornices, Full Landscaping (Front and back), exposed aggregated extended driveway and steps, NBN, floor to ceiling porcelain tiles in both bathroom, upgraded roof tiles, upgraded high doors, upgraded floor boards in bedroom, pendant lights, upgraded blinds, square sets, bulkheads, under mount sinks, upgraded tapware and showers have a lifetime warranty, freestanding bathtub, window splash back in the kitchen.
All this located in the highly sought after Estate which is surrounded by choice such as transport, schools, open space, cafes, Tarneit central and public transport, this modern contemporary lifestyle represents outstanding value as a brilliant investment opportunity and home owners alike.
Enduring and elegant, with a real sense of family comfort, this is a home that you cannot pass up seeing. Your earliest inspection is highly recommended.

Just off Leakes Rd and walking distance to Allure Estate, Westbrook estate, Truganina P 9 school , St Clairs School , Truganina East P-9 and Thomascarr School.

Description:
4 Beds, 2 Bath, 2 Kitchens with secure Dual income.
Endless possibilities with this neat and tidy brick home in an excellent location in Deer Park. Firstly, an outstanding block of land measuring approx. 700 m2 making future development possibilities high on any agenda (STCA). The property is currently set up as two tandem properties highlighting the dual income to the savvy investor (current gross rental return of $3324), with separate kitchen, bathroom and laundry facilities for each side of the house. Overall the property offers plenty of accommodation with 4 bedrooms in total, two separate living areas, two bathrooms and two kitchens. Neat and tidy yards and multiple car accommodation with an extra-large undercover car port.
Located in a fantastic location providing easy access to all local amenities including Deer Park Train station, Bon Thomas Reserve and sports ground, Deer Park North Primary School, local shops and cafes and minutes to the Western Ring Road .
With such huge potential for home buyers, renovators, investors and developers this unusual offering is an absolute rarity!

This is the home you've always wanted.

Exclusive. Exquisite. Exceptional.
Multiple living areas with wetlands as the backyard view, low maintenance design with practical living elements. This is an exquisite family home located in an exceptional address in Sanctuary Lakes, Point Cook.
The ground floor features an extensive zoned living area which includes a study and lounge which can potentially to be converted to a 5th bedroom, kid's play room or even a home mini home theater.
The modern Butler's Kitchen which is fully equipped with all necessities and appliances including stainless steel oven, dishwasher and plenty of storage space in the pantry. The first floor showcases a total of four spacious bedrooms with wardrobe space. The third living room extends to the balcony, overlooking the sky view and tranquility that Sanctuary Lakes has to offer. Additional features including heating, cooling, double-space garage and many more.
Sanctuary Lakes offers superior lifestyle facilities that include a gymnasium, indoor swimming pool, tennis courts, cafes in addition to dedicated cycling/walking trails that surround the scenic lake and parkland. This is more than a home. It's a lifestyle. Call us and register your interest now!

Description:
Grand Central Station
This property is close to all the essentials that is required for a perfect location. (East Facing)
From childcare to university, you will have a wide selection to choose from, giving your kids plenty of opportunities to learn, make friends and have a childhood full of stories
Shops, medical centre's, malls, dental clinics, all the major banks, Tarneit Post Office, restaurants, vet centre's, gyms and a major hospital. Everything you need is on your doorstep.
Grand central is serviced by not one, but two train stations Tarneit Station and Wyndham Vale Station. And by car, you will have a choice of freeways and major arterial roads linking you to Melbourne, Geelong, west to the ranges and east to the bay.
Settling May - 2020

Description:
Lot 2757 Newmarket Road PREMIUM - THE PROMENADE Collection 3
Create an enviable lifestyle at The Promenade, the gateway to the exceptional Riverwalk Premium within the established Riverwalk community in dynamic Werribee. Surround yourself with natural beauty in this exclusive parkside setting where more than 100,000 sqm of lush Riverfront parkland is just five minutes walk away.
The Promenades impressive entry features a wide tree-lined boulevard delivering a unique opportunity to nestle your dream home amongst mature trees and street landscaping. Enjoy an active lifestyle with the utmost convenience with Lollipop Creek and the Village Park within easy walking distance. A shared path will connect you to the Federation Trail that meanders beside the Werribee River for a scenic journey into the heart of Werribee. Take advantage of regular bus services to the suburbs flourishing amenity from a bus stop right on your doorstep. A premium parkside lifestyle by the river awaits at The Promenade.
A project by Development Victoria. Visit myriverwalk.com.au

Description:
TITLED LAND Lot 2533 - kalindi Street (Riverwalk)
Build your dream home sooner on this titled lot at Riverwalk.
Fresh thinking and thoughtful design are at the forefront of the Riverwalk. Here, you can choose a new way of life on the banks of the Werribee River. Contemporary architecture nestles into natural surrounds and amenities are easily accessible.
Within Riverwalk itself, the planned town centre will feature a variety of shops and cafes. With direct access to the Princes Freeway and moments from public transport, you'll get where you need to easily. Youll also enjoy being close to the Werribee Town Centre, shops, schools, public transport and more.
